Accessible seating is available for wheelchairs and companions.  There is a 4 ticket limit for all accessible seating, unless otherwise posted.

Wheelchair patrons should purchase 1 wheelchair seat as their seat and up to 3 companion seats.  Wheelchair companions should also purchase wheelchair seats as their seat.

Please Note: Hearing impaired patrons should contact the box office directly to purchase tickets to ensure additional accommodations are in place.  The box office can be reached by phone at (513) 621-8383 during regular business hours.

Accessible seats are located in Sections 101, 120, 146, 303, 307, 315, 337, 339 and 347 of the stadium.  More information is available by calling (513) 621-8383 during normal business hours or on game days at the Customer Service windows of the North Ticket Office located by Gate C.

Wheelchair patrons should purchase 1 wheelchair seat as their seat and up to 3 companion seats.  Wheelchair companions should also purchase wheelchair seats as their seat.

Please Note: Hearing impaired patrons should contact the box office directly to purchase tickets to ensure additional accommodations are in place.  The box office can be reached by phone at (513) 621-8383 during regular business hours.

Accessible seats are located in Sections 101, 120, 146, 303, 307, 315, 337, 339 and 347 of the stadium.  More information is available by calling (513) 621-8383 during normal business hours or on game days at the Customer Service windows of the North Ticket Office located by Gate C.

info.1:
Accessible seating is available for wheelchairs and companions.  There is a 4 ticket limit for all accessible seating, unless otherwise posted.

Wheelchair patrons should purchase 1 wheelchair seat as their seat and up to 3 companion seats.  Wheelchair companions should also purchase wheelchair seats as their seat.

Please Note: Hearing impaired patrons should contact the box office directly to purchase tickets to ensure additional accommodations are in place.  The box office can be reached by phone at (513) 621-8383 during regular business hours.

Accessible seats are located in Sections 101, 120, 146, 303, 307, 315, 337, 339 and 347 of the stadium.  More information is available by calling (513) 621-8383 during normal business hours or on game days at the Customer Service windows of the North Ticket Office located by Gate C.
